.pricing-faq
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-5.col-md-offset-1
        %dl
          %dt
            Do I need to pay now?
          %dd
            No. Sign up for a trial now, and pay when the trial ended or when you're ready.
          %dt
            Do I need a credit card to sign up for the trial?
          %dd
            No. We do not collect credit card information when you sign up for a trial account. Enter it when you’re ready to upgrade your plan.
          %dt
            What happens at the end of my trial?
          %dd
            Subscribe to Tueetion if it is right for you. If not, there’s no need to cancel anything. Your account becomes inactive, but your data remains intact in case you decide to subscribe at an another time.
          %dt
            Is there any limitation with the trial account?
          %dd
            There's no limitation in trial account.
      .col-md-5
        %dl
          %dt
            Can I add additional students in the middle of the month?
          %dd
            Sure you can.
          %dt
            What type of payment will you support?
          %dd
            We can only support transfer using Maybank2U and PayPal at the moment.
          %dt
            Is there time limit for the SMS credit?
          %dd
            No, your credit won't be expired.
          %dt
            I have more questions. Who do I ask?
          %dd
            Write us at hello@tueetion.com or call/WhatsApp us at (+60) 019-9171765. We’d be happy to chat with you.

